This file contains the intro animation sequence for Battlecruiser:3000AD.
If you did not download the BC3K30.ZIP file, then you must use SETUP21 to
configure the program. You can also configure the soundcard if you downloaded
either BC3KSB.ZIP or BC3KAD.ZIP.

To run the animation sequence, simply type BCINTRO

 - Supreme Commander [GALCOM]
